txt.en: 'Where is it that you come from?'
Register your heritage with the notary.
'Ah... Umbar.\n\n'You hail from Umbar, once a wealthy trading port and now home to the dreaded Corsairs. Its current rulers worship Sauron, but its people still yearn for freedom.'
Speak with Bonnie Milkweed, the notary
Bonnie Milkweed can be found in the Bree-town Hall.
